Package: ShapCOA
Type: Package
Title: Shapley Values Via Component Order of Addition Designs Et Al.
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Date: 2026-06-10
Author: David W. Lyon <dlyon@aurora2000.com>
Maintainer: David W. Lyon <dlyon@aurora2000.com>
Description: Use Component Order of Addition (COA) experimental designs to compute highly accurate approximations i
    of Shapley Values (SVs), even for very large number of items.
    Compute exact SVs for smaller problems.  
    Applicable to any underlying analysis, but highly optimized for common marketing resarch applications 
    (key driver regressions, total unduplicated reach and frequency or 'TURF' analyses, and 'TURF on MaxDiff').
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
